cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CR 

The paper deals with the problem of vehicle re-identification, which is a subfield of computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of deep learning models for vehicle re-identification, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper proposes a new benchmark dataset for vehicle re-identification, which could be relevant to researchers working in the areas of machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
